I just want her to be happy.

435
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:53,840
我们需要张照片
We'll need a photo.

436
00:42:57,000 --> 00:43:00,040
是个恶作剧 都是胡闹
It was mischief. A prank.

437
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:05,120
