请随意使用我办公室里的电话 请
Feel free to use the phone in my office. Please.

547
00:53:16,820 --> 00:53:19,020
Jenny 嗨
Jenny, hi.

548
00:53:19,020 --> 00:53:20,420
你认识这张图吗?
Do you know this picture?

549
00:53:23,180 --> 00:53:24,300
认识
Yeah.

