00:53:25,580 --> 00:53:27,820
她家里墙上挂着一张
She had one hanging on the wall at the home.

551
00:53:29,020 --> 00:53:31,260
她在别处还有吗?
Did she have one anywhere else?

552
00:53:33,180 --> 00:53:34,340
我怎么知道?
How would I know?

553
00:53:38,820 --> 00:53:42,060
车后面放着一具尸体时 恶魔桥走起来挺长的
Devil's Bridge is a long way to go with a body in the back of the car.

554
00:53:42,060 --> 00:53:44,140
你不担心被抓吗?
Weren't you worried about being caught?

555
00:53:44,140 --> 00:53:45,500
从没想过
Never thought about it.

556
00:53:46,580 --> 00:53:47,740
为什么选恶魔桥 Jenny?
Why Devil's Bridge, Jenny?

557
00:53:50,660 --> 00:53:53,260
我们是坏孩子时 她就是在那接我们
It's where she took us when we'd been bad.

558
00:53:54,300 --> 00:53:58,420
走到尽头...说恶魔住在那
Down the bottom... said the Devil lived there.

559
00:54:00,060 --> 00:54:02,340
如果我们不忏悔
If we didn't repent 

560
00:54:02,340 --> 00:54:05,620
他就会取走我们的灵魂 让我们在地狱永世燃烧
he'd take our souls and we'd burn in Hell for ever.

